  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<FormulaAbstract>

    public class FormulaSoft
extends FormulaHard
    Defines a soft formular. A soft formular is a conjunction of positive or negative literals assigned with a weight. At the moment this is restricted to a positive weight.
    Author:
    jan
